---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Search Engine Optimization - SEO for B2B Manufacturers | Square Root SEO" description="On-page, technical, and off-page SEO built for B2B manufacturers. Rank on Google for your industrial keywords and generate qualified leads organically." activePage="seo">

<section class="page-hero service-hero--foundry">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <span class="cmn-tag p1-bg">Core Service</span>
    <h1>Search Engine <span class="p1-clr">Optimization</span></h1>
    <p class="page-hero__sub">On-page, technical, and off-page SEO built around B2B industrial keywords. We make your manufacturing business rank where buyers actually search.</p>
    <div class="service-hero__badges">
      <span class="service-badge"><i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass-chart"></i> On-Page SEO</span>
      <span class="service-badge"><i class="fa-solid fa-code"></i> Technical SEO</span>
      <span class="service-badge"><i class="fa-solid fa-link"></i> Off-Page SEO</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="service-includes">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-title text-center reveal">
      <span class="cmn-tag p1-bg">What's Included</span>
      <h2>Complete SEO Strategy for Manufacturers</h2>
      <p style="max-width:650px; margin:10px auto 0; color:var(--text-muted);">Keyword research, technical fixes, link building. Everything your manufacturing site needs to rank on Google and bring in organic leads.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-cards-grid service-cards-grid--three">
      <div class="service-detail-card reveal">
        <div class="service-detail-card__icon" style="background:rgba(32,109,255,0.08);"><i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass p1-clr"></i></div>
        <h3>On-Page SEO</h3>
        <p class="service-detail-card__tagline">Keyword Foundation &amp; Content Optimization</p>
        <ul class="service-detail-card__list">
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Deep keyword research (50+ industrial keywords)</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Title tags &amp; meta descriptions optimised for every page</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Header tag (H1-H6) structure and hierarchy</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Image alt-text optimisation</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Internal linking strategy</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Schema markup for products &amp; organisation</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="service-detail-card__outcome">
          <strong><i class="fa-solid fa-bullseye p1-clr"></i> Outcome:</strong>
          Every page on your site is optimised to rank for the keywords your B2B buyers are searching.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-detail-card reveal">
        <div class="service-detail-card__icon" style="background:rgba(255,181,37,0.08);"><i class="fa-solid fa-code p3-clr"></i></div>
        <h3>Technical SEO</h3>
        <p class="service-detail-card__tagline">Site Health &amp; Crawlability</p>
        <ul class="service-detail-card__list">
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Full technical SEO audit and fixes</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> XML sitemap and robots.txt configuration</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Page speed optimisation</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Mobile-first indexing compliance</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Core Web Vitals improvement</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Google Search Console setup and monitoring</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="service-detail-card__outcome">
          <strong><i class="fa-solid fa-bullseye p3-clr"></i> Outcome:</strong>
          Google can discover, crawl, and index your pages correctly, so rankings can actually happen.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-detail-card reveal">
        <div class="service-detail-card__icon" style="background:rgba(236,25,30,0.08);"><i class="fa-solid fa-link p2-clr"></i></div>
        <h3>Off-Page SEO</h3>
        <p class="service-detail-card__tagline">Authority Building &amp; Link Strategy</p>
        <ul class="service-detail-card__list">
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Off-page SEO and link building strategy</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Google E-E-A-T compliance and authority signals</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Competitor analysis and gap identification</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Google My Business setup and optimisation</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Monthly SEO reporting and keyword tracking</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Content gap and opportunity analysis</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="service-detail-card__outcome">
          <strong><i class="fa-solid fa-bullseye p2-clr"></i> Outcome:</strong>
          Build domain authority and trust signals that push your pages to Page 1 for competitive keywords.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="page-cta reveal">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <h2>Ready to <span class="p1-clr">Rank on Google?</span></h2>
    <p>We'll build an SEO plan that puts your manufacturing business in front of buyers who are ready to buy.</p>
    <div style="display:flex; justify-content:center; gap:20px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-top:30px;">
      <a href="/contact" class="common-btn p1-bg box-style">Get Started <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right-long"></i></a>
      <a href="/acid-test" class="common-btn p3-bg box-style" style="color:var(--n900-clr);">Take Free ACID Test <i class="fa-solid fa-flask-vial"></i></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
